@startuml
title Import CSV/Excel + ML - Vue simplifiee

skinparam shadowing false
actor "Utilisateur" as User
participant "Angular" as Front
participant "API Spring Boot" as API
participant "FastAPI ML" as ML
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Front : Importer fichier
Front -> API : POST /api/transactions/import
API -> API : Lire CSV/Excel
API -> ML : POST /predict
ML --> API : Categorie + confiance
API -> DB : Enregistrer transactions
API --> Front : Resume import
Front --> User : Resultat
@enduml
